        "text": "<h2>Product Information</h2><ul><li>80 self-dissolving micro-darts in each patch that melt into the skin for deeper ingredient delivery</li><li>Stay comfortably for 2-6 hours, or overnight for best results</li><li>Continually works to give a rejuvenated look to your skin</li></ul>",
