        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Usage Instructions",
        "text": "<h2>Usage Instructions</h2><p><strong>How to Use:</strong></p><ol><li>After cleansing, simply peel off the adhesive strips.</li><li>Gently press for 5-10 seconds. The micro-darts dissolve the concentrated serum directly into the skin!</li><li>Wear for at least two hours. For best results, leave them on overnight!</li></ol>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
