        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Product Claims & User Study",
        "text": "<h2>Product Claims & User Study</h2><p>Key claims:</p><ul><li>Self-dissolving micro-darts infuse serum below the skin's surface for enhanced absorption and faster results.</li><li>Patches self-dissolve in as little as two hours, providing powerful results quickly.</li><li>Effectively treats fine lines, wrinkles, dark circles, puffiness, and under-eye bags.</li><li>Ultimate all-in-one patches that contain science backed, age-defying ingredients such as retinol, caffeine, niacinamide, licorice, and peptides for brighter-looking, smoother-feeling skin.</li></ul><p>Results from an independent user study:</p><ul><li>90% reported under-eyes were visibly brighter</li><li>77% saw a reduction in wrinkles</li><li>87% would recommend Micro-Infusion Targeted Patches to a friend</li></ul>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
