        "heading": "Creative Direction",
        "text": "<h2>Creative Direction</h2><p>Recording Guidelines</p><ul><li>Use bright, natural lighting. No filters.</li><li>Please do not wear makeup (unless to show makeup removal).</li><li>Show the Micro-Infusion Targeted Patches being peeled off, especially under the eye and show the micro darts in detail.</li><li>Keep backgrounds clean and uncluttered.</li><li>In cover photos for video content always show yourself using the Qure Micro-Infusion (unless agreed otherwise).</li><li>Before and after imaging to showcase the results, if possible</li></ul>",
